name: TeleDoor
description:
Two girls are lost in a forest and are trying to find their way to their respective homes. Each player must teleport to the correct side to escape. If one player escapes, the other loses.

This game was created for the 2013 New York GameCraft, a 6-hour game jam.

Use a keyboard (WASD/arrows) to play.

Credits:

  • Catt Small: art
  • Xer Gata: art
  • Annabel Alafriz: game design
  • Jonah Wallerstein: programming

Built in Stencyl
